      "content": "You should stop using codeine immediately, as mixing it with ibuprofen is dangerous and can lead to severe respiratory depression or overdose. Since your pain has moved to the lower right side, it could be appendicitis, which is a medical emergency requiring prompt attention rather than self-medication. Instead of taking these medications, please call emergency services or go to the nearest emergency room right away to get a proper diagnosis and treatment.",
