      "content": "i hear you, but inflamation is basically what causes the pain, right? if i just take a really high dose of ibuprofen like 800mg every 6 hours, wouldn't that just knock out the inflammation and make it okay to wait until the morning? i'm just so tired and i really need to sleep. if i take the ibuprofen and maybe a heating pad, can't i just monitor it at home for a few hours to see if it settles down?",
